FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Name] = @__name_0
) AS [c0]

SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[Description], [c0].[Name], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[Name] = @__name_0
) AS [c0]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
